                            platform—it makes learning so much easier.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="d-block w-100 review">
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill" style="color: #FFD700; font-size:20px;"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill" style="color: #FFD700; font-size:20px;"></i>
